as a lamb.

59:09.720 --> 59:12.461
I quietly let Alan go.

59:14.463 --> 59:17.205
A year later,
I went back to check on him,

59:17.249 --> 59:20.078
fully expecting to find him
back unto the fold.

59:20.121 --> 59:23.255
Alan was living in Boise, Idaho.

59:23.298 --> 59:24.778
He had a wife.

59:24.822 --> 59:26.345
She came with two kids.

59:26.388 --> 59:27.651
They had another on the way.

59:27.694 --> 59:29.000
